-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

All the code can be found in the src/ directory. The programs depend on Python
and the Natural Language Toolkit (http://www.nltk.org).

The following programs are provided:

test_model.py --      Main program for running the classifier against test cases.
                      Usage: test_model.py [-v] <train-dir> <test-dir>

train-k.py --         10-fold CV on the training data for determining the
                      discounting constants of the model.

Happy testing!
